  "title": "Preschool Cook (5 days)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Able to prepare nutritious meals suitable for children aged 2 months to 6 years</li>\n  <li>Keep the dining area clean and tidy after every meal or tea break</li>\n  <li>Design and plan monthly lunch menus, working closely with food vendors for quality provision</li>\n  <li>Support teachers by supervising children during their meal and tea breaks</li>\n  <li>Handle general cleaning of the pantry and utensils</li>\n  <li>Maintain a safe and hygienic environment in the infant care bay</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
